TXT_HEROS_INFO: Hero Unit Info Display
TXT_HEROS_INFO_DESC: Show individual icons for hero units in the top‑right corner. Click an icon to select the unit (if in a vehicle, select the vehicle). If already selected, center the view. Show health bar, shield bar, and Iron Curtain remaining time (if the unit is being produced, show production progress instead). If the unit is under Iron Curtain, display a semi‑transparent black overlay; if health is low, display a faint red glow; when attacked, briefly show a semi‑transparent red overlay; when attacking, show a semi‑transparent yellow overlay; when being designated for airstrike, show a persistent semi‑transparent red overlay; when being locked by Chrono weapons, show a persistent semi‑transparent blue overlay; when being drained by a Disc or magnetically controlled, show a persistent semi‑transparent purple overlay; when under EMP, show a persistent semi‑transparent gray overlay; when inside a vehicle or Tank Bunker, show a blue ring around the health bar. When inside a vehicle, health bar, shield bar, and Iron Curtain time are replaced by those of the vehicle.
TXT_HEROS_VISIBLE: Hero Unit Info Display: On
TXT_HEROS_INVISIBLE: Hero Unit Info Display: Off
