Description:DHB: [Side] Erebus - Ares Order
  [Unit Type] T2 Guerilla Tank
  [Armor] Heavy
  [Weapons]
    [108mm Shell]
    - Damage Type: Armor‑Piercing (AP)
    - Anti‑armor, anti‑building
    [Only Pain Can Repay]
    - Damage Type: Self‑Damage
    - Use when deployed; instantly drains 33% current health and grants 2x firepower and armor for a short period
