LoadBrief:Confederation: The Atlas Confederation (AC) focuses on nuclear technology and excels at harassment and raids; the radiation from its equipment is deadly to vehicles and infantry.
LoadBrief:Russians: Soviet Russia (RU) has a unique dual‑tech path (choose one). Build the [Tesla Assembly Plant] along the Tesla line to research Tesla tech, using EMP to paralyze enemy vehicles and buildings; build the [Field Intelligence Bureau] along the industrial line to unlock industry tech, excelling in frontal combat.
LoadBrief:China: The Eastern United Front (EUF) has the world's most advanced missile systems, using Iron Curtains and missile defense, plus superweapons for extreme long‑range strikes. It has strong frontline resilience and attrition capability.
LoadBrief:Europa: The Europa Joint Council (EJC) focuses on defense, excelling at ambushes and fortified positions, with reliable heavy armor and sturdy emplacements.
LoadBrief:Americans: The United States of America (USA) is renowned for its powerful air force and precision orbital strikes, with an arsenal built around aggressive laser weaponry and superior fire control systems.
LoadBrief:Pacific: The Pacific Island Chain (PIC) fields a frontline force based on cryo and nano technology, emphasizing long‑range firepower and amphibious operations, with strong battlefield support capabilities.
LoadBrief:YuriMind: The Psychic Mandate (EPM) has supernatural technologies feared worldwide, using powerful psychic and gravity fields to control the battlefield; its hero unit can even control buildings.
LoadBrief:YuriGen: The Chaos Legion (ECL) specializes in gene‑editing, recombining enemy infantry DNA to cause mutations that disrupt the battlefield, or enhancing their own infantry for superior individual combat power.
LoadBrief:YuriVirus: The Ares Order (EAO) focuses on biochemical weapons, deploying custom viruses to cause chaos; large‑scale poison gas is an infantry's nightmare.
