renwu:sov00910: Qianzhi: "I'm sure you've noticed, how could the Soviets have such a well‑equipped base? There may be more to this."
renwu:sov0096: Qianzhi: "Anyway, in this mission another general will lead the main assault; your job is to build a stable military base."
