renwu:sov00911: Qianzhi: "These are captured missile vehicles – they can shred enemy heavy armor and fortifications from range. Use them wisely."
renwu:sov00924: Qianzhi: "Hmm... but they seem damaged. Try to repair them with Engineers."
renwu:sov00925: Hint: Order Engineers to enter the Hongjian Missile Vehicles.
renwu:sov00926: Tianyu: "No good – this tank's armor is too thick. I can't snipe its driver. Maybe missiles would work?"
renwu:sov00927: Hint: Tianyu's sniper rifle cannot snipe Apocalypse Tank drivers – you need other units to deal with it.
