Description:TipsRussians: Tip: Soviet Russia revolves around EMP – use it well to turn the tide!
Description:TipsConfederation: Tip: The Atlas Confederation excels at guerrilla warfare – harass early, or suffer later!
Description:TipsChina: Tip: Don't let the Eastern United Front reach late game, or you'll be eating ICBMs QAQ
Description:TipsAmericans: Tip: Don't underestimate American laser weapons and air power – they handle both steel tides and guerrilla forces with ease.
Description:TipsBritish: Tip: The Maginot Line is no joke – try attacking the Europa Joint Council's fortifications if you dare.
Description:TipsAlliance: Tip: If you're planning a polar expedition, try some of the Pacific Island Chain's cryo technology first~
Description:TipsYuriMind: Tip: When you see a tank with a brain, remember one word: "Run"!
Description:TipsYuriGen: Tip: Erebus "fitness" technology – you can trust it!
Description:TipsYuriVirus: Tip: No matter how many infantry attack, the Ares Order leaves only clouds of poison gas.
THEME:SrLiYueRemix: Xianzhou & Liyue Battle Remix
renwu:all00911: Allied intel: "The MCV and supplies have arrived and are now under your command. Our satellite has locked this area, so we've regained the map."
Description:Tip9: "An Iron Curtain has descended across the European continent." – Winston Churchill
Description:Tip10: "Strategy is the brain, tactics are the limbs – both are indispensable." – Military proverb
Description:Tip11: "Technology is the primary combat power; innovation is the eternal theme." – Military maxim
Description:Tip12: "The steel tide crushes obstacles, precision strikes hit the vital points." – Military maxim
Description:Tip13: "War is the continuation of politics; the art of war lies in the hearts of men." – Military proverb
Description:Tip14: "All warfare is based on deception; surprise wins." – The Art of War
Description:Tip15: "The human brain is a Pandora's box full of electric charge – we are just beginning to understand it." – Yuri
Description:Tip16: "In all warfare, engage with the orthodox, win with the unorthodox." – The Art of War
Description:Tip17: "The highest form of warfare is to outthink the enemy; next is to outmaneuver; next is to outfight; the lowest is to besiege cities." – The Art of War
Description:Tip18: "There is no constant form in war, just as there is no constant shape to water – the one who can adapt to the enemy and win is divine." – The Art of War
Description:Tip19: "Victory and then standing strong, so the world submits." – Sun Bin's Art of War
Description:Tip20: "Momentum is what makes soldiers fight." – Sun Bin's Art of War
Description:Tip21: "Split them apart, then concentrate and strike." – Sun Bin's Art of War
Description:Tip22: "The four essentials of war: formation, momentum, change, and power." – Sun Bin's Art of War
Description:Tip23: "Know the enemy and know yourself, and you will never be defeated." – The Art of War
Description:Tip24: "All warfare is based on deception." – The Art of War
Description:Tip25: "Speed is valued in war, not duration." – The Art of War
Description:Tip26: "Without timing, terrain, and harmony of men, even victory brings disaster." – Sun Bin's Art of War
Description:Tip27: "Avoid the solid and strike the weak." – The Art of War
Description:Tip28: Did you know? Command & Conquer: Dawn of War was first publicly released on June 12, 2022~
Description:Tip29: "Meet soldiers with soldiers, block water with earth." – Battle of Paitong
