Description:WEIXING: Reveals terrain under fog of war via satellite
Description:ForceShield: Protects buildings in a small area from all damage
  But causes a base blackout for a period
Description:SpyPlaneSpecial: Summons a Spy Plane at a designated location
  Reveals fog of war it passes over
Description:ForceShieldUnit: Provides an energy shield to units in range (excluding buildings)
  The shield is considered heavy armor and can absorb 200 damage
Description:PsyReveal: Reveals terrain under fog of war
Description:Chrono: Select units in a 3x3 area and choose a target location
  Teleports units to that location
  Teleporting infantry kills them (except Chrono Legionnaires)
  Cannot teleport buildings
Description:Storm: Controls the weather in an area
  Target area is covered by storm clouds
  Lightning strikes periodically
Description:Iron: Makes vehicles in a 3x3 area invulnerable
  Lasts for a duration
  Cannot target infantry and kills them
Description:NukeSpecial: Weakened atomic bomb
  Devastates the target area
  Sirens sound in the target area
  [Psychic Sensor] can predict its impact point
Description:D14SP: The Eastern United Front's ultimate weapon
  Launches 6 ICBMs with thermonuclear warheads
  Cannot be fired into fog of war
Name:GCSpecial: Genetic Mutation
Description:GCSpecial: Deals area damage; killed infantry mutate into Brutes
Description:PDS: Permanently mind‑controls enemy units in range (including vehicles, infantry, and buildings)
  Also deals heavy psychic suppression damage (effective even against mind‑control immune units)
