    - Used only in Form I
    [EMP Missile PRO]
    - Damage Type: High Explosive (HE)
    - Anti‑armor, anti‑building
    - Reduces enemy movement and attack speed by 40% for a duration (non‑stackable)
    - Inflicts a 2‑second area EMP effect
    - Used only in Form I
    [Electronic Countermeasure System (Improved)]
    - Damage Type: EMP
    - Deploys full‑jamming ECM, losing mobility
    - Reduces speed and attack of all enemy armored units in range by 60%
    - Increases attack speed of friendly [Qilin Breaker Tanks] in range by 50%
    - Provides protection for all friendly units in range (15% chance to evade damage, non‑stackable)
    - Used only in Form II
  [Special Properties]
  - Immune to all crushing
  - Auto‑repairs
  - Can be permanently upgraded by support superweapon [Xiyue: Electronic Module Upgrade]
  - Limited to 9 (shared before/after upgrade)
  - Can enter Tank Bunkers
  - Immune to gravity effects
  - Deploy to switch between Form I and Form II
