RENWU:wdsov02easy: Location: Kiev – Dnieper River
  Difficulty: Easy
RENWU:wdsov02medium: Location: Kiev – Dnieper River
  Difficulty: Normal
RENWU:wdsov02difficult: Location: Kiev – Dnieper River
  Difficulty: Hard
RENWU:wdsov02s1: Eva: "Comrade General, our temporary defenses are complete."
RENWU:wdsov02s2: Eva: "This is our first defensive line."
RENWU:wdsov02s3: Eva: "The first line is commanded by Colonel Mikhail, tasked with stopping the Allies' first wave."
RENWU:wdsov02s4: Eva: "However, judging by the Europa Joint Council's momentum, one line won't hold long."
RENWU:wdsov02s5: Eva: "So you need to defend the second and third lines. Kiev's local forces are limited; the nearest Ural group is rushing here at full speed."
RENWU:wdsov02s5: Eva: "Before they arrive, make full use of local military facilities to hold off the Europa Joint Council."
RENWU:wdsov02s6: Eva: "To the southeast, across the Dnieper, lies Kiev."
RENWU:wdsov02s7: Eva: "If Kiev falls, Stalingrad will be wide open with no defenses. Stalingrad is our vital supply base and transport hub – its strategic importance is clear."
RENWU:wdsov02s8: Eva: "If we can hold them off, we'll have enough time to fortify Leningrad, Stalingrad, and Moscow."
RENWU:wdsov02s9: Eva: "Wait... it seems the Europa Joint Council's first wave is starting."
RENWU:wdsov02s10: Eva: "According to earlier intelligence, the Allies have retrofitted all their old equipment – performance and armor have improved significantly."
RENWU:wdsov02s11: Eva: "It's just the vanguard, and our first line is already close to breaking."
RENWU:wdsov02s12: Eva: "They've started massing their second wave – we need to reinforce our lines quickly!"
RENWU:wdsov02stime: Time until Ural group arrives:
Name:WDSOV02: Military Operation: Kiev Defense – Location: Ukraine – Kiev – Dnieper River
LoadMsg:WDSOV02: Military Operation: Kiev Defense – Location: Ukraine – Kiev – Dnieper River
LoadBrief:WDSOV02: >Primary Objective: Hold the line until the Ural group arrives.
  >Primary Objective: Destroy the Europa Joint Council's forward base.
Brief:WDSOV02: The Allies have officially declared war, and the Europa Joint Council has launched the first attack on the Western front.
  They are clearly well‑prepared; we could only hastily build a temporary defensive position. Losing Kiev would be disastrous – we must hold it!
