Name:T51LASER: Shock Commando
Description:T51LASER:  [Side] Allied Nations - Pacific Island Chain
  [Unit Type] Control Support Infantry
  [Armor] Helmet
  [Weapons]
    [Sonic Shock Cannon]
    - Damage Type: Sonic
    - Anti‑defense tower, anti‑infantry, anti‑building
    - Can knock back targets
  [Special Properties]
  - Immune to normal crushing
Name:MTNKE: Grizzly Medium Tank - Improved
Description:MTNKE: [Side] Allied Nations - Europa Joint Council
  [Unit Type] T1 Basic Tank
  [Armor] Medium
  [Weapons]
    [105mm AP Main Cannon]
    - Damage Type: Armor‑Piercing (AP)
    - Anti‑armor, anti‑building
    - 50% chance to deal extra damage
    - Can instantly kill targets below 25% health
  [Special Properties]
  - Can crush infantry
  - Can fire on the move
  - Can enter Tank Bunkers
  - Upgraded by protocol [Heavy Armor Division]
Name:OGQW: Eileen
Description:OGQW: [Side] Allied Nations - Europa Joint Council
  [Unit Type] Hero Unit
  [Armor] Helmet
  [Weapons]
    [Glory Drone]
    - Damage Type: Prism
    - Anti‑building, anti‑infantry, anti‑armor
    - Deploys up to 4 drones
    - Drones return to Eileen when out of ammunition or about to be destroyed
    [Defender Drone]
    - Damage Type: Autocannon
    - Can target air
    - Anti‑missile
  [Special Properties]
  - Limited to 1
  - Immune to mind control and nerve gas
  - Auto‑regenerates health
  - Immune to all crushing
  - Detects stealth or submerged units (range: 10)
  - Training speed not affected by multiple barracks
Name:QUEEN: Queen‑class Mothership
Description:QUEEN: [Side] Erebus
  [Unit Type] Infiltrator Unit
  [Armor] Heavy
  [Weapons]
    [Psychic Energy Cannon]
    - Damage Type: High Explosive
    - Anti‑infantry, anti‑armor, anti‑building
    - Large area damage
    - Inflicts [Wraith] on enemies:
      Speed reduced, deals percentage area damage when destroyed
  [Special Properties]
  - Obtained by infiltrating enemy [Allied Battle Lab]
  - Explodes on death
  - Auto‑repairs
Name:YMST: Moonstone Assault Vehicle
Description:YMST: [Side] Erebus
  [Unit Type] Infiltrator Unit
  [Armor] Heavy
  [Weapons]
    [Psychic Gravity Field]
    - Damage Type: Gravity + Psychic
    - Instantly kills infantry, anti‑armor, anti‑building
    - Fear: Causes hit enemy units to enter [Fear] state
    - [Fear]: Reduces enemy fire rate and attack power
    [Charge]
    - Deploy to use, grants 2x speed and 1.5x defense for a short time
    - Long cooldown
  [Special Properties]
  - Obtained by infiltrating enemy [Erebus Battle Lab]
  - Can crush infantry
  - Driver cannot be killed
  - Immune to mind control
  - Auto‑repairs
