Name:SXME: Cronos Railgun
Description:SXME: [Side] Erebus
  [Unit Type] Infiltrator Unit
  [Armor] Heavy
  [Weapons]
    [Psychic AP Cannon]
    - Damage Type: Armor‑Piercing (AP)
    - Anti‑infantry, anti‑armor, anti‑building
    - Penetrates enemies in a straight line
    [Backup Hidden Power Source]
    - Damage Type: High Explosive (HE)
    - Anti‑infantry, anti‑armor, anti‑building
    - Explodes on death
  [Special Properties]
